comment: Capela (HOU) sets the screen on DeRozan (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
DeRozan (TOR) legally contests Harden's (HOU) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.

[Observable in enhanced video] RHH shows that Beverley (HOU) has his right foot OOB while he is in contact with the ball. The officials are looking for any illegal contact and do not pick up his foot OOB.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the officials determined that the foul by DeRozan (TOR) met the criteria for a Flagrant Foul 1.
